com.adobe.xmp.schema.rng.model

Class Context

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.xmp.schema.rng.model.Context

  • public class Context
extends java.lang.Object
    The input schema definition file can define multiple XMP schemas. Each of those schemas defines multiple properties. The context stores an information holder for current property and current schema.
